      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Test workflow setup\n1. Import `Web Search - Brave API + Reader`.\n2. In the main workflow, open **Brave Web Search** and re-select your Brave Header Auth credential if needed.\n3. Copy the imported main workflow ID from its URL.\n4. Paste it into **Call Web Search Reader Workflow**.\n5. Run this test manually. Expected duration is roughly `readTopN × readerDelaySeconds` plus Reader latency.",
